{"tid":1037724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【3屍命案】男童過去一周病假缺席 校長：家長經常參加親子活動","createTime":"2019-02-26T06:49:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T06:54:35.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a61f246185725ed90af05b0d399e6e8622d89a5a","tid":1037724,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T06:49:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190226/59304798\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190226%2F59304798&d=%2BPHBpHGgTFxyg2LnQdSnfVQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=053086b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190226%2F59304798&h=746cc434\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190226/59304798</a><br />\n<br />\n3屍命案慘死的7歲男童「皓仔」，在薄扶林道香港潮商學校讀二年班。校長對事件感到難過，指「皓仔」自上周一請病假後，一直沒有返學，不料猝然離世，師生深表難過。而印象中「皓仔」父母十分愛錫兒子，三口子經常一齊參加學校的親子活動。<br />\n相關新聞：【3屍命案】單位變<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">凶宅</span> 街坊心慌慌<br />\n<br />\n詹漢銘校長稱，校方得悉事件後已經啟動危機應變小組，由社工及教育心理學家跟進學童情緒，暫時有數名同學因事件情緒較波動，要特別留意照料，校方亦發家長信，通知家長以留意子女狀況。<br />\n校長稱，「皓仔」小一入讀該校，成績和操行也良好。他的祖母今早親自到學校交代事件，校方得悉她只剩一名親友，既傷心又徬徨，將會盡量協助辦理身後事，並聯絡社會福利署提供協助。<br />\n相關新聞：西營盤夫婦燒炭亡 7歲子<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">陪死</span><br />\n<br />\n原來「皓仔」自上周一（18日）因為腸胃炎入院請病假，假紙至後天（28日），因此過去一星期已沒有上學。其間老師電話聯絡過家長，了解其病情，並沒察覺異樣。<br />\n校長指，「皓仔」父母報稱做文員及<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">地產公司經紀</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，過去也有出席學校的活動，包括旅行和運動會，印象中兩人也很友善。校長憶起「皓仔」的校園點滴，不禁掉下淚來，他指部份與「皓仔」相熟的老師也很傷心。"},{"pid":"29be04d88c5ee12e964bc870ba34db0030d868a1","tid":1037724,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T06:51:46.000Z","msg":"緊係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢老母要識多d人周圍乞人買樓嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa714e45ee7c62d901d86a5b9a86460a79d4d8c","tid":1037724,"uid":65346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T06:54:35.000Z","msg":"AA 自殺潮開始了...<br />\n政府可能已經研究全面取締 AA 狗行業<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}